{"tid":258930,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"計回報率","createTime":"2017-05-26T13:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-01T01:19:32.000Z","uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74b5a97c1668e162b62f0a2ba1cf4881aa1b3bb3","tid":258930,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:47:33.000Z","msg":"如果一開始投資$1,000,000，第一年後資產升值至$1,040,000，拎左$30,000出黎洗，其餘錢（即係$1,010,000）繼續投資，第二年後資產升值至$1,110,000，拎左$60,000出黎洗，其餘錢又繼續投資，第三年後資產升值至$1,060,000，全部cash out，咁平均每年投資回報率點計？"},{"pid":"710c0646ca10f2e41f4effd573a676ef7ef0fa6b","tid":258930,"uid":76426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T13:50:41.000Z","msg":"賺咗嘅錢除返咁多年 有幾難呀"},{"pid":"28d0a57a5f32fe76c3dcec86188507668d599d0c","tid":258930,"uid":66157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:09:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果一開始投資$1,000,000，第一年後資產升值至$1,040,000，拎左$30,000出黎洗，其餘錢（即係$1,010,000）繼續投資，第二年後資產升值至$1,110,000，拎左$60,000出黎洗，其餘錢又繼續投資，第三年後資產升值至$1,060,000，全部cash out，咁平均每年投資回報率點計？</blockquote><br />\n點睇咁計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 40,000/1,000,000 =0.04<br />\n2. 100,000/1,010,000 =0.099<br />\n3. 10,000/1,050,000 =0.0095<br />\n(0.04+0.099+0.0095)/3"},{"pid":"47942f5a3cfc29262a8c349a05b00e129140ffdb","tid":258930,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:15:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e333101938654574aef49c810725737e84b11b","tid":258930,"uid":82382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:23:14.000Z","msg":"(1,040,000 - 1,000,000)/1,000,000 = 4%<br />\n(1,110,000 - 1,010,000)/1,010,000 = 9.9%<br />\n(1,060,000 - 1,050,000)/1,050,000 = 0.95%<br />\n<br />\n(1 + IRR)^3 = (1 + 4%) x (1 + 9.9%) x (1 + 0.95%)<br />\nIRR = 4.8855997%<br />\nCompounded Return = 4.89%"},{"pid":"14e3ff972ad11953db8db6238a40e1b41b33866f","tid":258930,"uid":115388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T15:26:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1881cd3ebb1d9f329cb10215c119b8a8c70b7c3b","tid":258930,"uid":29773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8bdc547dc5d338ab1b773c05dfc215c6f0c6ac3","tid":258930,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:10:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果一開始投資$1,000,000，第一年後資產升值至$1,040,000，拎左$30,000出黎洗，其餘錢（即係$1,010,000）繼續投資，第二年後資產升值至$1,110,000，拎左$60,000出黎洗，其餘錢又繼續投資，第三年後資產升值至$1,060,000，全部cash out，咁平均每年投資回報率點計？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你想計 Dollar weighted 定 Time weighted？"},{"pid":"df64459b0525eb58004a9fb45353beca7662a550","tid":258930,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T01:19:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果一開始投資$1,000,000，第一年後資產升值至$1,040,000，拎左$30,000出黎洗，其餘錢（即係$1,010,000）繼續投資，第二年後資產升值至$1,110,000，拎左$60,000出黎洗，其餘錢又繼續投資，第三年後資產升值至$1,060,000，全部cash out，咁平均每年投資回報率點計？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你想計 Dollar weighted 定 Time weighted？</blockquote><br />\nDollar weight"}]}